       TESTSUITE "HELLO WORLD TESTS"

       TESTCASE "MESSAGE IS SET CORRECTLY"
           MOVE "HELLO, WORLD!" TO WS-MESSAGE
           EXPECT WS-MESSAGE TO BE "HELLO, WORLD!"

       TESTCASE "COUNTER INCREMENTS"
           MOVE ZEROS TO WS-COUNTER
           ADD 1 TO WS-COUNTER
           EXPECT WS-COUNTER TO BE 1
